ğŸ¨ Frontend (Non-Dockerized)
The frontend is a static HTML/CSS setup you can preview using Live Server or any HTTP server.

ğŸ”§ Usage
Open the index.html or new-note.html file via Live Server.

Submit new notes via the form.

Data is posted directly to http://localhost:3000/api/add-note.

> Note: Ensure the backend is running before submitting the form!

